{"tid":654860,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【夫子IQ題】那一天，創意台終於回想起了，曾經一度支配他們的夫子，還有被迷惑於IQ題中的屈辱","createTime":"2018-05-06T04:16:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T08:33:10.000Z","uid":20032,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"2267a864435a72f34b4f32c6048d2905f118de35","tid":654860,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T04:16:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/618916/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/618916/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n是咁的，我上po輸左，還了創意台一月平安<br />\n<br />\n宜家我精氣神達到頂峰，窮思極想，要出一條難度比夫子高的一條IQ題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">男人偷窺女溫泉，猜一中國地方名</span><br />\n<br />\ntips:個地方唔係 &quot;廣州&rdquo; &ldquo;雲南&rdquo; 之類，係類似&ldquo;香港中文大學&rdquo; 地標性既地方<br />\n<br />\n幾肯定大家都聽過<br />\n<br />\n今日我剛回創意台，就不下賭資了<br />\n<br />\n祝Q運亨隆"},{"pid":"715fd39f9f49783bd91b7d5c65daa212618ce84f","tid":654860,"uid":20032,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T04:17:37.000Z","msg":"夫子一請謎語人"},{"pid":"9226c684bd5c800783891a80929db0fa07a7c27b","tid":654860,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T04:18:06.000Z","msg":"二請諸葛忠武侯孔明"},{"pid":"f290866ea289bc2eef4dc01137d58c5f0951cdf8","tid":654860,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T04:18:54.000Z","msg":"三請青帝太昊伏羲"},{"pid":"7c23bc26236e9b2cd486bb11095d27617ac6c2bf","tid":654860,"uid":126507,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T04:23:11.000Z","msg":"cls 咁難點諗！"},{"pid":"8ca5348b2efcb66785462421e1ccc2f64ed5df4f","tid":654860,"uid":62532,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T04:23:54.000Z","msg":"寧波， 因為入面全部港女"},{"pid":"13f47dc8ca17cbdc5597dd2d57cb00b6dc0082a3","tid":654860,"uid":20032,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8ca5348b2efcb66785462421e1ccc2f64ed5df4f","tid":654860,"uid":62532,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-